ComicInfo.Summary: On a desperate mission to find a way to keep a dear friend safe, mighty mage Monty finds himself outmatched by a blade spider, an ether-eating ancient biomechanical horror. So he calls in a top squad for aid: Gina, Britanny, Ace, Barrette, and Charlotte. But when they arrive, they find their foe already viciously subdued by something. Something powerful. Something elusive. Something with a curious dislike for "birdies"...
